<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/corporate-officers-of-the-house-of-lords> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The House of Lords is the second chamber of UK Parliament. It plays a crucial role in examining bills, questioning government action and investigating public policy. Corporate Officers of the House of Lords is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Cabinet Office ."@en .
